\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
为了检查振幅虚部的来源，来观察传播子的虚部：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\imm\frac{1}{p^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon}=\frac{1}{2i}\left(\frac{1}{p^{2}-m^{2}+i\varepsilon}-\frac{1}{p^{2}-m^{2}-i\varepsilon}\right)=\frac{-\varepsilon}{(p^{2}-m^{2})^{2}+\varepsilon^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

除了在
\begin_inset Formula $p^{2}=m^{2}$
\end_inset

附近发散，当
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon\to0$
\end_inset

，式子趋于零。如果我们对
\begin_inset Formula $p^{2}$
\end_inset

积分，我们发现
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{\infty}\dd p^{2}\frac{-\varepsilon}{\left(p^{2}-m^{2}\right)^{2}+\varepsilon^{2}}=-\left.\arctan\left(\frac{p^{2}-m^{2}}{\varepsilon}\right)\right\vert _{0}^{\infty}=-\pi
\]

\end_inset

暗示了
