的积分回路，这一项给出零。另外，两个
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数的项没法同时满足。在静止系中最容易看出，
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}=0$
\end_inset

 so that 
\begin_inset Formula $p^{0}=M$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{k-p}=\omega_{k}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $k^{0}=M+\omega_{k}\,\&\&\,k^{0}=\omega_{k}$
\end_inset

无法同时满足。丢掉这些为零的项，得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
i\mathcal{M}_{\text{loop}}(p^{2})=-\frac{\lambda^{2}}{2}\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\left[\Pi_{F}(k-p)\frac{\pi}{\omega_{k}}\delta(k^{0}-\omega_{k})+\Pi_{F}(k)\frac{\pi}{\omega_{k-p}}\delta(k^{0}-p^{0}-\omega_{k-p})\right]
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数为实数，所以虚部之可能来自于费曼传播子。因此，计算
\begin_inset Formula $\imm\mathcal{M}_{\text{loop}}(p^{2})$
\end_inset

 相当于
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\imm\mathcal{M}_{\text{loop}}(p^{2}) & =-\frac{\lambda^{2}}{2}\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\Bigg[\pi\delta\left((k-p)^{2}-m^{2}\right)\frac{\pi}{\omega_{k}}\delta(k^{0}-\omega_{k})\\
 & +\pi\delta\left(k^{2}-m^{2}\right)\frac{\pi}{\omega_{k-p}}\delta(k^{0}-p^{0}-\omega_{k-p})\Bigg]
\end{align*}

\end_inset

第二行的两个
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数仍然没法同时满足，所以为零。所以我们使用
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{2\omega_{k}}\delta(k^{0}-\omega_{k})=\delta(k^{2}-m^{2})-\frac{1}{2\omega_{k}}\delta(k^{0}+\omega_{k})
\]

\end_inset

并由于
\begin_inset Formula $\int\dd k^{0}\delta\left((p-k)^{2}-m^{2}\right)\delta(k^{0}+\omega_{k})=0$
\end_inset

，最终写成一个简单的形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
2\imm\mathcal{M}_{\text{loop}}(p^{2})=-\frac{\lambda^{2}}{2}\int\frac{\dd^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\left(-2\pi i\right)\delta\left((k-p)^{2}-m^{2}\right)\left(-2\pi i\right)\delta\left(k^{2}-m^{2}\right)\label{eq:24.33}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

这个方程表明,通过让中间粒子在壳，可以计算出振幅的虚部。从这里更容易看出为什么可以作替换。在静止系中，
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}=0$
\end_inset

 so that 
\begin_inset Formula $p^{0}=M$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{k-p}=\omega_{k}$
\end_inset

, 两个
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数共有四个零点，
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
k^{0}=M\pm\sqrt{\omega_{k}},\quad k^{0}=\pm\sqrt{\omega_{k}}
\]

\end_inset

考虑到
\begin_inset Formula $M>0$
\end_inset

，在四种组合中
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
M+\sqrt{\omega_{k}} & =\sqrt{\omega_{k}},\quad M+\sqrt{\omega_{k}}=-\sqrt{\omega_{k}},\\
M-\sqrt{\omega_{k}} & =\sqrt{\omega_{k}},\quad M-\sqrt{\omega_{k}}=-\sqrt{\omega_{k}},
\end{align*}

\end_inset

只有
\begin_inset Formula $k^{0}=M-\sqrt{\omega_{k}}\quad\&\quad k^{0}=\sqrt{\omega_{k}}$
\end_inset

是有可能实现的，也就是
\begin_inset Formula $2\sqrt{\omega_{k}}=M$
\end_inset

。也就是创造两个
\begin_inset Formula $\pi$
\end_inset

粒子的阈值。容易看出，也就是要求粒子的能量为正数。
\end_layout

